---
// Route Preview Component - Bilingual
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">
          52公里转山路线
        </h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
          52km Kora Circuit
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8" data-lang-content="zh">
          三天两夜的高原徒步，从塔尔钦出发，翻越5630米的卓玛拉垭口，最终回到起点。这是一段身体与心灵的双重旅程。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
          A 3-day high-altitude trek from Darchen, crossing the 5,630m Dolma La pass, returning to the starting point. A journey of both body and soul.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-kailash-dark font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="zh">第一天：塔尔钦 → 止热寺（20km）</h3>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Day 1: Darchen → Drirapuk (20km)</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">平缓起步，适应海拔，沿途可见神山北壁</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Gentle start, altitude acclimatization, view of Kailash's north face</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-kailash-dark font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="zh">第二天：止热寺 → 尊珠寺（18km）</h3>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Day 2: Drirapuk → Dzultripuk (18km)</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">翻越卓玛拉垭口，最具挑战的一天</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Crossing Dolma La pass - the most challenging day</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-kailash-dark font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="zh">第三天：尊珠寺 → 塔尔钦（14km）</h3>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Day 3: Dzultripuk → Darchen (14km)</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">轻松返程，完成神圣的转山之旅</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Easy return, completing the sacred kora</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/routes" class="inline-flex items-center mt-8 text-kailash-gold font-semibold hover:text-kailash-accent transition">
          <span data-lang-content="zh">查看详细路线</span>
          <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">View Detailed Route</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/kailash-aerial.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-kailash-gold text-kailash-dark p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium" data-lang-content="zh">海拔高度</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Elevation</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold">4,560m - 5,630m</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>